Villain: Gufufu... What a fine figure you cut, Lord Shark!
I've been longing for this chance to get my revenge on you!!
Here, take this ticket!

Memimi: (This guy... isn't he the villain I beat to a pulp
in Monster Fight before...? This is bad... even someone like
him...)

Henchman: What's wrong, Lord Shark!? Where's your greeting
to our boss, Goblin Ninja-sama? We're gonna upload this to
the net, so you better serve us properly, huh?

Henchman: This is payback for the hangout spot you took from
us in Monster Fight!! We're gonna spread videos of you
moaning and writhing from our boss's dick all over the
world!

Memimi: (That was because you guys were partying in the
park's sandbox... No point in saying that now...)

Memimi: Excuse me, dear customer... Thank you for purchasing
the right to sex... Um, as for your preferred location... if
it's the hotel near the station, we have an affiliation with
them...

Villain: Who cares about an audience!! We're doing it right
here, right now! Strip off all your clothes... You're gonna
get fucked right here in the nude!

Memimi: (Don't cry... don't get angry, me... I must
endure... I won't lose to someone like this...! Even if I'm
violated, even in front of people, even if it's streamed...
Ahh...)
